@c    1:33. And the sons of Madian:  Epha, and Epher, and Henoch, and Abida,
@c    and Eldaa.  All these are the sons of Cetura.

@c    1:34. And Abraham begot Isaac:  and his sons were Esau and Israel.

@c    1:35. The sons of Esau:  Eliphaz, Rahuel, Jehus, Ihelom, and Core.

