@c    1:40. The sons of Sobal:  Alian, and Manahath, and Ebal, Sephi, and
@c    Onam.  The sons of Sebeon:  Aia, and Ana.  The son of Ana:  Dison.

@c    1:41. The sons of Dison:  Hamram, and Eseban, and Jethran, and Charan.

@c    1:42. The sons of Eser:  Balaan, and Zavan, and Jacan.  The sons of
@c    Disan:  Hus and Aran.

@c    1:43. Now these are the kings that reigned in the land of Edom, before
@c    there was a king over the children of Israel:  Bale the son of Beor:  and
@c    the name of his city was Denaba.

