@c    is, he that made the sun to stand.  In like manner the following names,
@c    Lying (Chozeba), Secure (Joas), and Burning (Saraph), are substituted
@c    in place of the Hebrew names of the same signification.

@c    4:23. These are the potters, and they dwelt in Plantations, and Hedges,
@c    with the king for his works, and they abode there.

@c    Plantations and Hedges. . .These are the proper names of the places
