@c    4:24. The sons of Simeon:  Namuel and Jamin, Jarib, Zara, Saul:

@c    4:25. Sellum his son, Mapsam his son, Masma his son.

@c    4:26. The sons of Masma:  Hamuel his son, Zachur his son, Semei his son.

@c    4:27. The sons of Semei were sixteen, and six daughters:  but his
