@c    Basan.

@c    5:13. And their brethren according to the houses of their kindreds,
@c    were Michael and Mosollam, and Sebe, and Jorai, and Jacan, and Zie, and
@c    Heber, seven.

@c    5:14. These were the sons of Abihail, the son of Huri, the son of Jara,
@c    the son of Galaad, the son of Michael, the son of Jesisi, the son of
@c    Jeddo, the son of Buz.

@c    5:15. And their brethren the sons of Abdiel, the son of Guni, chief of
@c    the house in their families,

@c    5:16. And they dwelt in Galaad, and in Basan and in the towns thereof,
