@c    trained up to battles, four and forty thousand seven hundred and
@c    threescore that went out to war.

@c    5:19. They fought against the Agarites:  but the Itureans, and Naphis,
@c    and Nodab,

@c    5:20. Gave them help.  And the Agarites were delivered into their hands,
