@c    6:63. And to the sons of Merari by their families out of the tribe of
@c    Ruben, and out of the tribe of Gad, and out of the tribe of Zabulon,
@c    they gave by lot twelve cities.

@c    6:64. And the children of Israel gave to the Levites the cities, and
@c    their suburbs.

@c    6:65. And they gave them by lot, out of the tribe of the sons of Juda,
@c    and out of the tribe of the sons of Simeon, and out of the tribe of the
