@c    11:34. Ahiam the son of Sachar an Ararite,

@c    11:35. Eliphal the son of Ur,

@c    11:36. Hepher a Mecherathite, Ahia a Phelonite,

@c    11:37. Hesro a Carmelite, Naarai the son of Azbai,

