@c    26:21. The sons of Ledan, the sons of Gersonni:  of Ledan were heads of
@c    the families, of Ledan, and Gersonni, Jehieli.

@c    26:22. The sons of Jehieli:  Zathan and Joel, his brethren over the
@c    treasures of the house of the Lord,

@c    26:23. With the Amramites, and Isaarites, and Hebronites, and
@c    Ozielites.

@c    26:24. And Subael the son of Gersom, the son of Moses, was chief over
@c    the treasures.

@c    26:25. His brethren also, Eliezer, whose son Rohobia, and his son
@c    Isaias, and his son Joram, and his son Zechri, and his son Selemith.

